%N A396453 Primes p such that p^2 - 2 is a prime and p^2 + 2 is a semiprime.
%C A396453 2, and primes p such that p^2 - 2 and (p^2 + 2)/3 are primes.
%H A396453 Robert Israel, <a href="/A396453/b396453.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000</a>
%e A396453 a(3) = 29 is a term because 29 is a prime, 29^2 - 2 = 839 is a prime, and 29^2 + 2 = 3 * 281 where 3 and 281 are primes.
%p A396453 filter:= t -> isprime(t) and isprime((t^2+2)/3):
%p A396453 filter(2):= true:
%p A396453 select(filter, [2, seq(op([6*i+1,6*i+5]),i=1..1000)]);
%Y A396453 Intersection of A062326 and A109953.
%K A396453 nonn,new
